</h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-43_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Organisations must adhere to specific legislative and regulatory requirements to effectively align with Creative Scotland's objectives. This ensures compliance and enhances the integrity and sustainability of their creative endeavours.



























</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-45_ pf-heading-1-h3"><strong> Legislation and regulations </strong></h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-47_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-48_ pf-text-1"><strong>Equality Act 2010</strong> - Promotes equal opportunities and prohibits discrimination in various fields, including employment and the provision of services. Creative organisations must ensure their policies and practices are inclusive and non-discriminatory.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-50_ pf-text-1"><strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong> - Governs the handling of personal data. Creative enterprises must implement robust data protection measures to secure personal information and respect individuals' privacy rights.






</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-52_ pf-text-1"><strong>Health and Safety at Work Act 1974</strong> - Require employers to ensure their employees' health, safety, and welfare. Creative organisations should conduct risk assessments and provide appropriate training to maintain a safe working environment.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-54_ pf-text-1"><strong>Copyright, Designs and Patents Act 1988</strong> - Protects the rights of creators over their original works. Creative organisations must understand and respect copyright laws to avoid legal infringements.







</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-56_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ilfuhL ejXpQB pf-57_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-58_ pf-heading-1-h3">Best practices for compliance
